hands_on_practices.solution:
我们要求相速度
$$v_p = \frac{\omega}{k} = \frac{c}{n} = \frac{c}{\sqrt{2}}
\;\Longrightarrow\;n^2 = 2.$$

X模的色散关系为
$$n^2 = \frac{RL}{S}
\;\Longrightarrow\;RL = 2S.$$
这里
$$R = 1 - \frac{\omega_{pe}^2}{\omega(\omega - \omega_{ce})},\quad
L = 1 - \frac{\omega_{pe}^2}{\omega(\omega + \omega_{ce})},\quad
S = 1 - \frac{\omega_{pe}^2}{\omega^2 - \omega_{ce}^2}.$$

计算乘积
$$RL = \frac{\bigl[\omega(\omega-\omega_{ce}) - \omega_{pe}^2\bigr]
\,\bigl[\omega(\omega+\omega_{ce}) - \omega_{pe}^2\bigr]}
{\omega^2(\omega^2 - \omega_{ce}^2)}
= \frac{(\omega^2 - \omega_{pe}^2)^2 - \omega^2\omega_{ce}^2}
{\omega^2(\omega^2 - \omega_{ce}^2)}.$$
以及
$$2S = 2\,\frac{\omega^2 - \omega_{ce}^2 - \omega_{pe}^2}
{\omega^2 - \omega_{ce}^2}.$$

令 $RL=2S$ 得
$$\frac{(\omega^2 - \omega_{pe}^2)^2 - \omega^2\omega_{ce}^2}
{\omega^2(\omega^2 - \omega_{ce}^2)}
= \frac{2(\omega^2 - \omega_{ce}^2 - \omega_{pe}^2)}
{\omega^2 - \omega_{ce}^2}.$$
两边同乘以 $\omega^2(\omega^2 - \omega_{ce}^2)$ 并化简：
$$\omega^4 - \omega_{ce}^2\omega^2 - \omega_{pe}^4 = 0.$$
令 $X=\omega^2$。则
$$X^2 - \omega_{ce}^2X - \omega_{pe}^4 = 0
\;\Longrightarrow\;
X = \frac{\omega_{ce}^2 \pm \sqrt{\omega_{ce}^4 + 4\omega_{pe}^4}}{2}.$$
取正根并利用 $\omega=\sqrt{X}$ 得出
$$\omega = \sqrt{\frac{\omega_{ce}^2 + \sqrt{\omega_{ce}^4 + 4\omega_{pe}^4}}{2}}
= \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\sqrt{\omega_{ce}^2 + \sqrt{\omega_{ce}^4 + 4\omega_{pe}^4}}.$$
